			<p><strong>How much do you charge for lessons?</strong></p>
			<p>Lesson prices are set by the instructor. The price will be displayed
				in the advertisement</p>
		</div> <!-- end of col-md-6 -->
		<div class="col-md-6">
			<p><strong>Can I pay the instructor in person?</strong></p>
			<p>You must pay for the lesson through the site.</p>
		</div> <!-- end of col-md-6 -->
	</div> <!-- end of row -->
</div> <!-- end of container -->